[12:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Sometimes the model may ignore lip-syncing, especially when using very short audio files. This is easily solved by activating the LoRA IC for lip-syncing on this node. We can extend the audio through a prompt, but it is essential that the Impaint option is selected in the audio track, and in this way we perform an Impaint but of audio.'

[12:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hello and welcome to a new video.'

