[13:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'We can also insert the LoRAs IC from each of the LTX Director guide nodes. This allows us, for example, to introduce one LoRA in the generation phase and a different LoRA in the expansion phase.'

[14:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Finally, we have the experimental tool Retake, which allows us to change the actions of a shot in videos that do not contain changes of scene, usually lasting only a few seconds. We enter Retake mode by pressing this button.'

[14:22] [scene:talk]
